lendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1864]] {{ill|April 26|ja|4月26日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Horita Masamutsumi|ja|堀田正睦|12=draft}}, a senior councilor (Rōjū) of the Tokugawa shogunate, died (born [[1810]]).
