== Deaths == * {{ill|Shōwa|ja|承和|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[835]] {{ill|April 22|ja|4月22日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – In this year, the monk {{ill|Kūkai|ja|空海|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (also known as Kōbō-Daishi), founder of the Shingon sect, is recorded as having died (note: some sources may differ on dates). * {{ill|Kashō|ja|嘉祥|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[850]] {{ill|May 6|ja|5月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Nimmei|ja|仁明天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 54th Emperor of Japan, died (born [[810]]). * {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1650]] {{ill|April 21|ja|4月21日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The famous swordsman and Kenjutsu master {{ill|Yagyū Sanjūrō|ja|柳生三厳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (also known as Yagyū Jūbei) died (born [[1607]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1822]] {{ill|May 12|ja|5月12日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Matsudaira Saitō|ja|松平斉恒|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 8th lord of the Matsue Domain, died (born [[1791]]). * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1864]] {{ill|April 26|ja|4月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Horita Masamutsumi|ja|堀田正睦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a senior councilor (Rōjū) of the Tokugawa shogunate, died (born [[1810]]).
