== Events == * {{ill|Daibō|ja|大宝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daibō|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[701]] {{ill|May 3|ja|5月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 3|qq=}}) – Following a gold offering from Tsushima, the era name was changed to {{ill|Daibō|ja|大宝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daibō|qq=}}. * {{ill|Kannin|ja|寛仁|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannin|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1019]] {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 28|qq=}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michinaga|ja|藤原道長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara no Michinaga|qq=}} retired from court life and began the construction of {{ill|Muryōju-in|ja|無量寿院|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Muryōju-in|qq=}}. * {{ill|Genkyū|ja|元久|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genkyū|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1204]] {{ill|April 26|ja|4月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 26|qq=}}) – During the rebellion of the Taira clan on the 3rd day, known as the {{ill|Mikka Taira no Ran|ja|三日Taira Clanの乱|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mikka Taira no Ran|qq=}}, the forces of 【平賀朝雅】 subdued the remnants of the Taira clan in Iga and Ise. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 17th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1612]] {{ill|April 21|ja|4月21日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 21|qq=}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate issued a decree banning Christianity directly under its control; the measure was expanded nationwide the following year. == Births ==
